snippet.title: Penguin Platform
snippet.description:
Welcome to Penguin Platform - Penguin's home for bookish content for teens! Here you'll find videos filled with bookish chats, discussions, recommendations, giveaways & some special YouTuber guests.

Join our Discord full of YA and teen readers: https://discord.gg/zr9TGZH

Sign up to our YA newsletter for more exclusive chapters, giveaways and the latest book news: http://po.st/PlatformNewsletterSignUp

You can also find us on Twitter and Instagram @penguinplatform! 

Have any video requests or ideas? Just leave us a comment or get in touch on Twitter.

We're part of Penguin Random House UK.
